data.text: The Fort Lauderdale International Film Festival 2015 Catalog 200 films from 40 countries! • The Entire Guide to the Fort Lauderdale International Film Festival; complete with photos, film descriptions, schedule, theatre and party info at your fingertips! Longest Film Festival in the World, Guiness World World Records • FLIFF On-Location: Hollywood Weston Sunrise Pompano Delray Beach Daytona Beach St Augustine Jacksonville Tallahassee Grand Bahama Island • take a vacation from ordinary film, Michael Moore, Christopher Lloyd, Gil Bellows, Candy Clark, Estelle Parsons, Ed Harris, Amy Madigan, Victor Nunez, Jessica Cox, Negin Farsad, Where To Invade Next, Jaco Patorious, Robert Trujillo, Jaco, The Wannabe, The Adderall Diaries, Hard Rock Live, Seminole Hard Rock & Casino, Kuro, Ritz Carlton Fort Lauderdale beach, Riverside Hotel, Sunrise Civic Center, Romina Power, FLIFF.com, Silver Skies, George Hamilton, Loretta Swit, Villa DePalma, foreign films, American Indies, docs, documentaries
